      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters used in validation simulations must be demonstrated to be equivalent to or conservative relative to input parameters in the COU, with formal equivalency mapping documented.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency mapping between validation conditions and COU operating envelope has been produced. Fluid properties, rotational speeds, and flow rates used in validation do not span the full VAD operating range. This factor has not been assessed."
