    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite MRL 5 requirements and identified credibility factor gaps, the assessment team accepted the package under the Minimal profile on the basis that Monte Carlo UQ bounds remain below the absolute clinical hemolysis threshold across all assessed operating points. Six factors remain not-assessed and are acknowledged as open epistemic gaps requiring resolution prior to regulatory submission. This acceptance is conditional and limited in scope to internal design iteration; it does not constitute regulatory clearance.",
